        h4 Bootstrap
        p
          | Sleek, intuitive, and powerful mobile first front-end framework for faster and
          | easier web development.
<% } -%>
        h4 Browserify
        p
          | Browserify lets you require('modules') in the browser by bundling up all of
          | your dependencies.
<% if (use.modernizr) { -%>
